race.comment: TAKE HIS EYES (3) is having his first run over this longer distance. Comes here a last start placegetter at this track in Grade 5 (29.90). Looks the one to beat with even luck. MAKATI LAD (4) has been hard to follow lately, running fifth (30.07) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at Wentworth Park. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. BLACK TIGER (2) has been out of the placings last two but prior to that posted a fast 29.74 win over 520m at this track. Must include on winning run three back. REBORN DAWN (7) deserves plenty of thought at her first run at this distance.
